cast.overview: Recently fired and desperate for work, a troubled young man named Mike agrees to take a position as a night security guard at an abandoned theme restaurant: Freddy Fazbear's Pizzeria. But he soon discovers that nothing at Freddy's is what it seems.
cast.title: Five Nights at Freddy's

details.biography:
Grant is an American child actor, He is known for his work Obi-Wan Kenobi (2022), Creepshow (2019), and In the End (2021). He's birthplace is Birmingham, Alabama, USA. But he currently lives in Vestavia Hills, AL.

The young actor, who appeared as the young Luke Skywalker in the 2022 Lucasfilm / Disney Plus project Obi-Wan Kenobi series, will meet with the TV series and movie audiences in new projects.

- IMDb Mini Biography By: yusufpiskin
details.name: Grant Feely
